export var DistinctDays=function DistinctDays(cityForecastWeatherData){//Finding out all distinct dates in the five days forecast
var distinctDays=cityForecastWeatherData.list.map(function(forecastData){return new Date((forecastData.dt+cityForecastWeatherData.city.timezone)*1000).toLocaleDateString("en-US");}).filter(function(value,index,self){return self.indexOf(value)===index;});return distinctDays;};
